'''費利·威特曼'''（Ferry Weertman，{{bd|1992年|6月27日||}}）是一名[[荷兰|荷兰]][[游泳|游泳]]运动员<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.len.eu/Press/LEN%20-%20PR2-16%20LEN%20Awards%202015.aspx |title=LEN Awards 2015 |date=5 January 2016 |publisher=[[LEN|LEN]] |access-date=5 January 2016 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203163014/http://www.len.eu/Press/LEN%20-%20PR2-16%20LEN%20Awards%202015.aspx |archivedate=2016-02-03 }}</ref>，获得2016年[[里约奥运会|里约奥运会]]男子10公里公开水域游泳[[金牌|金牌]]。

==事业==
2014年赢得[[欧洲游泳锦标赛|欧洲游泳锦标赛]]10公里游泳冠军。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Holland Keeps Rolling In Open Water At European Championships With Men’s 10K Win |work=[[Swimming_World|Swimming World]] |date=14 August 2014 |url=http://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/holland-keeps-rolling-in-open-water-at-european-championships-with-mens-10k-win/ |accessdate=23 December 2015}}</ref>2015年赢得[[世界游泳锦标赛|世界游泳锦标赛]]10公里银牌。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Jordan Wilimovsky Wins Men’s 10K Open Water Race as USA Qualifies 2 to 2016 Rio Olympics |work=Swimming World |date=27 July 2015 |url=http://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/jordan-wilimovsky-wins-mens-10k-open-water-race-as-usa-qualifies-2-to-2016-rio-olympics/ |accessdate=23 December 2015 |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017080033/https://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/jordan-wilimovsky-wins-mens-10k-open-water-race-as-usa-qualifies-2-to-2016-rio-olympics/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年获得欧洲公开水域锦标赛10公里游泳冠军。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://swimswam.com/ferry-weertman-defends-european-10k-title-in-hoorn/ |title=Ferry Weertman defends European 10K title in Hoorn |first1=Braden |last1=Keith |date=July 10, 2016 |publisher=[[Swimswam|Swimswam]] |access-date=July 10, 2016 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108122054/https://swimswam.com/ferry-weertman-defends-european-10k-title-in-hoorn/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年8月16日，以1小时52分59.8秒的成绩赢得里约奥运会10公里游泳金牌。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sports.yahoo.com/news/rio-2016-weertman-snatches-victory-144309293.html |title=Rio 2016: Weertman snatches victory from Gianniotis in open water |date=August 16, 2016 |publisher=[[Yahoo|Yahoo]] |access-date=August 16, 2016 |archive-date=2018-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180809215744/https://sports.yahoo.com/news/rio-2016-weertman-snatches-victory-144309293.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

